title: Adult Nappy Bags - 200 Pack, 20% Thicker Sacks, Easy Tie Handles, Odour Free, Discreet White Plastic, Strong Sanitary Disposal Bag
features: STRONGER: Our high-quality nappy bags are manufactured from premium polyethylene plastic, offering a superior solution that is 10% thicker than normal bags. With a 20mu thickness, they provide exceptional strength and durability. These nappy sacks are unscented and odour free.

SIZE: Measuring 8 x 13 x 18 inches, our nappy bags are specifically designed to hold multiple nappy products. With a height of 18 inches (45cm), a width of 8 inches (20cm), and a width with side gussets of 13 inches (33cm), they offer ample space for convenient disposal.
DISCREET AND SECURE: Our nappy sacks provide complete discretion when disposing of nappy waste. You can trust that your privacy is protected with these sanitary disposal bags.

LONG HANDLES: Our adult nappy bags feature convenient 4.5-inch handles, making it easy to tie and carry them to the bin. Whether you're at home, on the move, outdoors, or traveling, these bags provide a secure and hygienic solution for nappy disposal.
